    </div>
    <button class="bg-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-300 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border-b-4 border-orange-700 hover:border-orange-500 rounded-lg m-2">ごほうびを編集する</button>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-amber-100 rounded-lg p-4 m-5">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold">総移動距離　km</div>
    <button class="bg-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-300 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border-b-4 border-orange-700 hover:border-orange-500 rounded-lg m-2">くわしく見る</button>
  </div>
</div>